<div class="category">
<h1 class="category__title">Korea Watch</h1>
<p><p><a href="https://twitter.com/GrecianFormula">Edited by Harry J. Kazianis</a>, the Center for the National Interest’s Korean Studies Senior Director and <em>TNI’s</em> Executive Editor, Korea Watch is our portal into all things Korea.</p>
<p>In this space, we will tackle issues such as the North Korea challenge, U.S.-DPRK relations, South Korean domestic politics and economic issues, technological innovations originating on the Korean peninsula, demographics and more.</p>
</p>
</div>
